<span id="freeTextContainer5026282751238759232">I always knew it was about race...but I never knew it was <i>so much about race</i>. US Conservatism is so close to that sly, ignorant kind of evil that it makes me shudder.<br/><br/>I&apos;m still trying to process this book, but I will say that there was a lot I expected, and a lot that I really hadn&apos;t expected <i>at all</i>.<br/><br/><br/>(Obviously I am a liberal and was before reading this)</span>
  <span id="freeText5026282751238759232" style="display:none">I always knew it was about race...but I never knew it was <i>so much about race</i>. US Conservatism is so close to that sly, ignorant kind of evil that it makes me shudder.<br /><br />I'm still trying to process this book, but I will say that there was a lot I expected, and a lot that I really hadn't expected <i>at all</i>.<br /><br /><br />(Obviously I am a liberal and was before reading this)</span>
