<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/62659.Profit_Over_People"><img alt="Profit Over People: Neoliberalism and Global Order" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1386924256l/62659._SX98_.jpg" />
